Fram here clicking on a journey allows you to edit or delete it Reporting Under 'Current Journey' click the 'Finish Journey' button. Completing a Journey ��Logging your mileage has never been easier. Simply click 'Current Journey' then click the + button. Enter some basic details about your journey you're about to start logging. Hit save and your app will begin logging your location Logging A Journey Back
